sentences: Cornelis Witthoefft (born 1964 in Hamburg) is a conductor and vocal coach, who was appointed professor of Lied (Art Song) at the State University of Music and Performing Arts Stuttgart (Musikhochschule Stuttgart, Germany) in 2004.

Cornelis Witthoefft (born 1964 in Hamburg) is a conductor and vocal coach, who was appointed professor of Lied (Art Song) at the State University of Music and Performing Arts Stuttgart (Musikhochschule Stuttgart, Germany) in 2004.
